      "span_text": "AprA and CfaD may activate BzpN by a mechanism independent of translocation, such as an activating phosphorylation that does not regulate subcellular localization, as is the case for the Arabidopsis bZIP transcription factor TRAB1 in response to the hormone abscisic acid"
